{"tid":727892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港女性格可以點樣改？","createTime":"2018-07-03T11:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T14:03:23.000Z","uid":154924,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b464b181315759e738feed25ef644c29decf853b","tid":727892,"uid":154924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"我同佢一齊左兩年 由識佢個刻我都冇刻意隱瞞過自己性格 都係咁港女 開心唔開心都擺曬上面 <br />\n<br />\n到左我地一齊 佢對我真係好好 好錫我 身邊每一個朋友都睇得出 包容我啲小脾氣容忍我會哄我 <br />\n<br />\n但之後個年 我地成日嗌交 大多都係小事  次次都可以嘈到分手 之後又係翻埋一齊 又嘈 不斷輪迴 <br />\n<br />\n但佢宜家已經唔想再哄我 有時候我都知啲小事唔應該嬲 但自己都唔知就嬲左 同埋都不過想佢哄下我 我有應承過佢會改 但性格呢家嘢真係好難改 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心求教 輕插plz <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c38c071d180ff42028679e30a24b60130c9852","tid":727892,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"嬲啲乜？有冇例子？"},{"pid":"87a110dca4a57fdf289b16f3924ccb39a18267b7","tid":727892,"uid":52942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"唔使改，搵個頂得順既"},{"pid":"8feb9ee0ef36943dd9e5322d155cddfa578eadeb","tid":727892,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"男人老狗有乜好鬧<br />\n大家互射打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3145a7019c0e9d931b47e48daa32e784e42bd6","tid":727892,"uid":85591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"唔使改，繼續做自己，下個會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9923c0ba2b8dbc5cd6b11a0ebd3a340d097888b2","tid":727892,"uid":29070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"下個更可愛"},{"pid":"f21753946f06f9bc2378bcb3f89a95fbc255ab5b","tid":727892,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07